<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 18:07:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国际刑事法院将于 2024 年 2 月就以色列在巴勒斯坦领土上的行为的后果举行听证会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/world-court-to-hold-hearings-on-consequences-of-israeli-practices-in-palestinian-territory/0000018b-5d70-d8e2-a1eb-ff7690810000</link><description>国际法院将于明年二月举行听证会，要求就包括东耶路撒冷在内的被占领土上的做法的法律影响提供咨询意见</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 17:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/world-court-to-hold-hearings-on-consequences-of-israeli-practices-in-palestinian-territory/0000018b-5d70-d8e2-a1eb-ff7690810000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列最需要帮助的时刻，内塔尼亚胡的右翼民粹主义朋友去了哪里？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-23/ty-article/.highlight/in-israels-hour-of-need-where-did-netanyahus-right-wing-populist-friends-go/0000018b-5d56-d8e2-a1eb-ff56076d0000</link><description>除了以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡令人震惊的一长串政治和概念失败之外，还要加上他对世界各地极右翼盟友深不可测、短视的信任</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 17:05:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-23/ty-article/.highlight/in-israels-hour-of-need-where-did-netanyahus-right-wing-populist-friends-go/0000018b-5d56-d8e2-a1eb-ff56076d0000</guid></item><item><title>公开情报显示美国向以色列、塞浦路斯和约旦部署了更多武器和部队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/u-s-deploys-more-arms-and-troops-to-israel-cyprus-and-jordan/0000018b-5cbf-d307-adbb-7dbf1aa80000</link><description>以色列和哈马斯爆发战斗以来，已有30多架美军重型运输机降落在以色列，载有高级官员、后勤装备或军事援助物资</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 15:12:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/u-s-deploys-more-arms-and-troops-to-israel-cyprus-and-jordan/0000018b-5cbf-d307-adbb-7dbf1aa80000</guid></item><item><title>我们应该将哈马斯的袭击与大屠杀进行比较吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/should-we-compare-the-hamas-assault-to-the-holocaust/0000018b-5cbb-d307-adbb-7dbb40b50000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 14:21:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/should-we-compare-the-hamas-assault-to-the-holocaust/0000018b-5cbb-d307-adbb-7dbb40b50000</guid></item><item><title>拜登对以色列加沙战争的支持是否会让他输掉 2024 年大选？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/could-bidens-support-of-israels-gaza-war-cost-him-the-2024-election/0000018b-5c62-d2b2-addf-7e7a1d6e0000</link><description>摇摆州的阿拉伯和穆斯林社区威胁不在明年的总统选举中投票给乔·拜登，巴勒斯坦裔美国众议员拉希达·特莱布带头谴责</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 14:07:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/could-bidens-support-of-israels-gaza-war-cost-him-the-2024-election/0000018b-5c62-d2b2-addf-7e7a1d6e0000</guid></item><item><title>这位以色列教授警告犹太父母不要让他们的孩子进入美国精英大学</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-professor-is-warning-jewish-parents-to-keep-their-kids-away-from-elite-u-s-colleges/0000018b-5c37-d8e2-a1eb-ff37fcba0000</link><description>哈马斯袭击以色列后，哥伦比亚大学的 Shai Davidai 教授公开表达了美国学术机构的安全担忧。他指责自己的大学校长未能打击校园内支持恐怖分子的学生组织</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 14:00:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-professor-is-warning-jewish-parents-to-keep-their-kids-away-from-elite-u-s-colleges/0000018b-5c37-d8e2-a1eb-ff37fcba0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯大屠杀之后，创伤治疗将不再一样</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dealing-with-national-trauma-after-hamas-attack-classic-psychotherapy-is-not-enough/0000018b-3e23-df22-a5eb-3f7b14f20000</link><description>哈马斯的突然袭击让以色列震惊不已。当事件正在进行并且现实感觉不安全时，治疗创伤的传统方法是不够的，但以色列人以同情心对待彼此肯定会有所帮助</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 13:43:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dealing-with-national-trauma-after-hamas-attack-classic-psychotherapy-is-not-enough/0000018b-3e23-df22-a5eb-3f7b14f20000</guid></item><item><title>歌手公开反对哈马斯大屠杀后，麦当娜的安保细节得到升级</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/madonnas-security-detail-upgraded-after-singer-speaks-out-against-hamas-massacre/0000018b-5c70-d00f-a9bf-7c78761b0000</link><description>这位已经开始全球庆祝巡演的歌手谴责了这起致命袭击，并写道“我的心与以色列同在”，她在社交媒体上受到了严厉的批评。</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 12:55:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/madonnas-security-detail-upgraded-after-singer-speaks-out-against-hamas-massacre/0000018b-5c70-d00f-a9bf-7c78761b0000</guid></item><item><title>破坏者成功地将特拉维夫从地图上抹去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/saboteurs-successfully-erase-tel-aviv-off-the-maps/0000018b-5b9d-d473-a5fb-7fdd33210000</link><description>OpenStreetMap 曾出现过编辑战争，用户反复恢复地图上已删除的部分，并阻止正在删除它们的用户。自第一次删除以来，已有数十次编辑和重建</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 12:20:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/saboteurs-successfully-erase-tel-aviv-off-the-maps/0000018b-5b9d-d473-a5fb-7fdd33210000</guid></item><item><title>在反犹太主义抬头之际，英国犹太人为在加沙被扣押的以色列人质举行集会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/british-jews-rally-for-israeli-hostages-held-in-gaza-amid-rising-antisemitism/0000018b-5c31-d8e2-a1eb-ff37966a0000</link><description>反犹太主义袭击增加了 1,350% 以上，犹太教堂和犹太学校加强了安全措施，但这并没有阻止英国犹太人，他们周日大批参加了伦敦特拉法加广场的示威活动</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 12:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/british-jews-rally-for-israeli-hostages-held-in-gaza-amid-rising-antisemitism/0000018b-5c31-d8e2-a1eb-ff37966a0000</guid></item><item><title>半岛电视台以色列办事处应该关闭吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/should-al-jazeeras-israeli-offices-be-shut-down/0000018b-5c36-d8e2-a1eb-ff36d6f60000</link><description>半岛电视台正在呼应哈马斯的信息，并且在报道上疏忽大意，但这是否证明以色列政府有理由关闭该电视台的运作——正如沙特阿拉伯、埃及和伊拉克已经所做的那样？</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 11:44:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/should-al-jazeeras-israeli-offices-be-shut-down/0000018b-5c36-d8e2-a1eb-ff36d6f60000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷两家豪华酒店拒绝接待遭受哈马斯袭击的以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/two-jerusalem-luxury-hotels-refuse-to-house-israelis-struck-by-hamas/0000018b-5bf9-d473-a5fb-7ff991c90000</link><description>阿尔弗雷德·阿基洛夫拒绝向因战争而流离失所的数千名以色列人开放马米拉和大卫城堡酒店的大门；他的解释是：缺乏人手。他还拒绝了旅游部提供的帮助招聘员工的帮助</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 11:22:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/two-jerusalem-luxury-hotels-refuse-to-house-israelis-struck-by-hamas/0000018b-5bf9-d473-a5fb-7ff991c90000</guid></item><item><title>为什么右翼美国不是以色列的真正盟友</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-right-wing-america-is-no-real-ally-for-israel/0000018b-5bfd-d00f-a9bf-7bfdd4ae0000</link><description>对于美国右翼专家和政客来说，煽动反对拜登、移民和穆斯林远比真正声援以色列人和支持以色列安全重要得多</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 11:05:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-right-wing-america-is-no-real-ally-for-israel/0000018b-5bfd-d00f-a9bf-7bfdd4ae0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列能否从最可怕的噩梦中醒来并采取正确的行动？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/can-israel-wake-up-from-its-worst-nightmare-and-do-the-right-thing/0000018b-56e0-d2b2-addf-76f84b5d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 11:04:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/can-israel-wake-up-from-its-worst-nightmare-and-do-the-right-thing/0000018b-56e0-d2b2-addf-76f84b5d0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管一再警告，以色列军队忽视了加沙边境发生故障的观测气球</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/despite-warnings-idf-neglected-malfunctioning-observation-balloons-on-gaza-border/0000018b-5b84-d8e2-a1eb-fb96f45b0000</link><description>仍在运行的所有四个气球都遭到哈马斯的攻击并击落，操作它们的士兵（现在集中在数量较少的操作室中）无法传递信息并警告部队</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 10:52:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/despite-warnings-idf-neglected-malfunctioning-observation-balloons-on-gaza-border/0000018b-5b84-d8e2-a1eb-fb96f45b0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯扣押的人质代表将与以色列外长埃里·科恩一起出席联合国安理会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-live/world-leaders-tell-israel-to-adhere-to-international-law-gaza-running-out-of-fuel/0000018b-5a5d-d00f-a9bf-7a5da4e10000</link><description>美国报道称，拜登政府建议以色列推迟加沙地面行动，以利人质获释 ■ 土耳其要求哈马斯领导人在 10 月 7 日袭击后离开其领土 ■ 以色列国防军称，加沙有 222 人质被扣为人质，其中包括“相当多”外国人 ■ 紧张局势恢复以色列国防军袭击真主党小组时在北部边境 ■ 第三支援助车队进入拉法过境点进入加沙 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，哈马斯至少造成 1,300 人死亡 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：4,380 名巴勒斯坦人死亡，13,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 09:52:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-live/world-leaders-tell-israel-to-adhere-to-international-law-gaza-running-out-of-fuel/0000018b-5a5d-d00f-a9bf-7a5da4e10000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙，以色列正奔向道德深渊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-gaza-israel-is-racing-to-the-moral-abyss/0000018b-57d1-d8e2-a1eb-f7d7dc100000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 09:52:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-gaza-israel-is-racing-to-the-moral-abyss/0000018b-57d1-d8e2-a1eb-f7d7dc100000</guid></item><item><title>15万枚导弹瞄准以色列：真主党的致命武器库能达到多远</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/150-000-rockets-and-missiles-the-weapons-israel-would-encounter-in-a-war-with-hezbollah/0000018b-573d-d2b2-addf-777df6210000</link><description>根据最新的已知评估，真主党拥有深入以色列境内的火箭和远程导弹、广泛的防空系统和突击队</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 07:18:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/150-000-rockets-and-missiles-the-weapons-israel-would-encounter-in-a-war-with-hezbollah/0000018b-573d-d2b2-addf-777df6210000</guid></item><item><title>中东紧张局势加剧，以色列军队等待入侵加沙的命令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-awaits-order-for-gaza-invasion-as-middle-east-tensions-sear/0000018b-58f5-dd05-a7bf-ffffe0550000</link><description>随着伊朗试图针对以色列和美国的利益、也门叛乱分子向以色列发射导弹以及真主党使边境升温，美国在该地区部署了大量军事存在。内塔尼亚胡的圈子传达的信息是，最好不要急于进入加沙，担心发生大规模火灾</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 05:48:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-awaits-order-for-gaza-invasion-as-middle-east-tensions-sear/0000018b-58f5-dd05-a7bf-ffffe0550000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-5a6c-d473-a5fb-7eedd9540000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 02:47:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-5a6c-d473-a5fb-7eedd9540000</guid></item></channel></rss>